# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- Complete open source governance setup
- Issue and PR templates
- Support documentation
- Security policy
- Code of conduct
- Contribution guidelines
- Roadmap planning

### Changed
- Updated SECURITY.md with bug bounty program
- Enhanced documentation structure
- Improved test coverage

### Fixed
- Minor documentation typos
- Test configuration issues

## [0.1.0] - 2024-01-01

### Added
- Initial public release
- Core compliance program with all instructions
- Complete TypeScript SDK
- Token Extensions integration
- Comprehensive documentation and examples
- Test suite with CI/CD
- Basic open source files

### Features
- Investor registration and management
- Compliance policy configuration
- Transfer validation via Token Extensions
- Wallet freezing/unfreezing
- Admin controls and multi-sig support
- Country restrictions and KYC levels
- Batch operations and utilities

### Security
- PDA-based account security
- Input validation and error handling
- Admin authorization checks
- No upgrade backdoors

## Roadmap

See [ROADMAP.md](ROADMAP.md) for detailed future plans.

### Upcoming Releases

