---

## Versioning Scheme

- **MAJOR** version for incompatible API changes
- **MINOR** version for added functionality (backwards compatible)
- **PATCH** version for bug fixes

## Deprecation Policy

Features will be marked as deprecated for one MINOR version before removal.
Migration guides will be provided for breaking changes.

## Release Cadence

- **Patch releases**: As needed for bug fixes (weekly)
- **Minor releases**: New features (monthly)
- **Major releases**: Breaking changes (quarterly)

## Migration Guides

Major version updates include migration guides in the documentation.
EOF